---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Blob from "../../components/Blob.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="About Us"
    description="Learn more about Montessori-Kinderhaus Potsdam West, our team and our pedagogy."
    locale="en"
>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative py-16 md:py-24 px-4 md:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold mb-6">
                About Us
            </h1>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
                Since October 2002 we have been supporting children in Potsdam
                West on their journey – following the principles of Maria
                Montessori and with great commitment from our parent initiative.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- History Section -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 md:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h2
                        class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-4"
                    >
                        Our History
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        The Montessori-Kinderhaus opened its doors in October
                        2002 in Potsdam West, near Sanssouci Park. Since then it
                        has been run by the association "Montessori-Kinderhaus
                        Potsdam e.V." as a parent initiative.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
                        What began as a small initiative is today a vibrant
                        place for up to 66 children from their first birthday
                        until school entry. Our success is built on the mindful
                        collaboration of educators, children and dedicated
                        parents.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="relative">
                    <Blob
                        class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-full h-full opacity-40"
                        variant="cream"
                    />
                    <img
                        src="/images/photos/IMG_0144.webp"
                        alt="Kinderhaus exterior"
                        class="relative z-10 w-full rounded-2xl object-cover object-center"
                        style="aspect-ratio: 4/3;"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pedagogy Section -->
    <section id="paedagogik" class="py-16 px-4 md:px-8 bg-cream-dark">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-8">
                Our Pedagogy
            </h2>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
                        The Child at the Centre
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
                        We see every child as a whole person. Our educators see
                        themselves as companions and observers, not instructors.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
                        Free Choice of Activities
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
                        Children follow their sensitive periods and interests at
                        their own pace. The prepared environment enables
                        independent action.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
                        Experiencing Boundaries
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
                        Children experience boundaries through the order of the
                        room, the materials themselves and living together with
                        others – quite naturally.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
                        Respect & Tolerance
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
                        We foster mutual respect and peaceful coexistence.
                        Social learning happens in the group, complementing the
                        family.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
                        Diversity & Inclusion
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">
                        We welcome and embrace diversity as an enrichment. Our
                        Kinderhaus is barrier-free and our team includes
                        specialists in inclusive care.
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="/en/diversity"
                        class="text-yellow-dark hover:text-text transition-colors font-medium text-sm"
                    >
                        More about Diversity & Inclusion →
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">
                <strong>Please note:</strong> Admission to our Kinderhaus does not
                guarantee admission to the Montessori secondary school, which operates
                independently.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Section -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 md:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-8">
                Our Team
            </h2>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Our team consists of <strong
                            >nine state-certified educators</strong
                        >, all of whom have completed or are completing
                        additional Montessori training. They are supported by
                        interns and dedicated parents.
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold mb-4">
                        Our Groups
                    </h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-muted">
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span
                                class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
                            ></span>
                            <span
                                ><strong>Toddler group:</strong> Children under 3,
                                cared for by 3 educators</span
                            >
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span
                                class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
                            ></span>
                            <span
                                ><strong>Mixed-age group 1:</strong> Age 2.5 to school
                                entry, 2 educators</span
                            >
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span
                                class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
                            ></span>
                            <span
                                ><strong>Mixed-age group 2:</strong> Age 2.5 to school
                                entry, 2 educators</span
                            >
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-yellow/20 rounded-2xl p-6">
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold mb-4">
                        Opening Hours
                    </h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-muted">
                        <li class="flex justify-between">
                            <span>Monday – Thursday</span>
                            <span class="font-medium">7:30 AM – 4:30 PM</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex justify-between">
                            <span>Friday</span>
                            <span class="font-medium">7:30 AM – 3:00 PM</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 md:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
            <div class="bg-yellow/30 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">
                    Get to Know Us
                </h2>
                <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
                    Visit us for an observation visit or at our next
                    get-to-know-us coffee.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="/en/registration"
                    class="inline-block bg-yellow hover:bg-yellow-dark text-text font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition-colors"
                >
                    Registration
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
